# Host-owned knowledge-chat NDJSON transcripts (runtime artifacts, never committed)
storage/knowledge-chat/
# The engine's durable run index (runId → logPath) — runtime state, never committed.
storage/knowledge-chat-state/
# Plant Doctor engine runtime artifacts: NDJSON logs, the codex-roles-verified state record, and the
# per-session workspaces that hold LIVE scoped JWTs (doctor-context.json) — NEVER committed.
storage/plant-doctor/
storage/plant-doctor-state/
storage/plant-doctor-workspaces/
# Staged raw upload bytes for the async photo worker (PHOTO_INBOX_DIR default) — runtime, never committed.
storage/photo-inbox/
# Secret-grade log-directory snapshots taken by promote-legacy-system-messages.ts --apply (conversation
# transcripts) — the rollback net for that migration, never committed.
storage/promote-legacy-system-messages-backups/
# Chat image attachment upload roots (agents-realtime 3.0.x uploadRoot for the knowledge-chat and
# plant-doctor engines) — durably stored user-attached photos under a 24h TTL, NEVER committed. This repo
# is public; the moment anyone attaches an image locally, git must not offer to commit a private photo.
storage/knowledge-chat-uploads/
storage/plant-doctor-uploads/
